---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cancellation & Refund Policy" description="Expert Guru's cancellation and refund policy for tutoring services.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 via-white to-secondary/10 py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We want you to feel confident choosing Expert Guru.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          At Expert Guru, we are committed to delivering high-quality tutoring services. We understand that circumstances can change, and we've designed our cancellation and refund policy to be fair and transparent.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Free Demo Class</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Every new student is entitled to one free demo class per subject. The demo class carries no obligation, and no payment information is required to book it. If you choose not to continue after the demo, there is nothing to cancel or pay.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We offer a 100% money-back guarantee for new students within the first four paid sessions or two weeks of starting the program, whichever comes first. If you are not satisfied with the quality of tutoring during this period, contact our support team and we will process a full refund.
            </p>
          </div> -->

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Class Cancellations by Students</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Students or parents may cancel or reschedule a scheduled session with the following guidelines:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>24+ hours notice:</strong> The session can be rescheduled at no charge.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Less than 24 hours notice:</strong> The session may be marked as completed or a late cancellation fee may apply, at the discretion of the Education Manager.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>No-shows:</strong> If a student misses a session without prior notice, the session will be counted as completed.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Class Cancellations by Expert Guru</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              In the rare event that Expert Guru needs to cancel a session (due to tutor unavailability, technical issues, or other unforeseen circumstances), the session will be rescheduled at no additional cost. If rescheduling is not possible, a credit or refund will be issued for the affected session.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Requests</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">To request a refund, please email us at <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@expertguru.net</a> with the following information:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Student name and parent/guardian name</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Registered email address</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Reason for the refund request</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Payment receipt or transaction ID</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Processing</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Approved refunds will be processed within 7–10 business days. Refunds will be issued to the original payment method. Please note that any bank processing fees are non-refundable.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Discontinuing Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Students may discontinue tutoring services at any time by notifying their Education Manager or emailing <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@expertguru.net</a>. There are no long-term contracts or cancellation penalties. You only pay for the sessions you use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Expert Guru reserves the right to modify this Cancellation & Refund Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Continued use of our services after changes are made constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions?</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90 mb-4">If you have any questions about our cancellation and refund policy, please don't hesitate to reach out:</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">Expert Guru</p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Email: <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="underline">info@expertguru.net</a></p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Website: <a href="https://www.expertguru.net" class="underline">www.expertguru.net</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
